# Normalise all text files to LF on checkout/checkin so that Prettier's
# default `endOfLine: "lf"` and the Linux-developed source tree behave
# identically on Windows runners (which otherwise apply CRLF via
# core.autocrlf and cause `prettier --check` to fail in CI).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must stay untouched.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.mcpb binary
